Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.93,0:22:22.63,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Let me guide you down into my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:28.88,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}And let us pray for the world to realize
