Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.75,0:22:41.89,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Emptiness  erodes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:47.86,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Coz you're free from pain and sorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.48,0:22:54.26,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Future is just too bright to show you ways
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:23:00.31,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\be1}Wake up now  it's time to lead new souls
